{"tid":1459194,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"錯就要認 唔認清自己錯誤 只會重覆犯錯","createTime":"2019-08-12T16:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T17:10:27.000Z","uid":59666,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d877b9e063ef88211be98133583e08356766aa1e","tid":1459194,"uid":59666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:28:32.000Z","msg":"我唔否定今日行動有部份效果 今日所有野都做得好好 除咗中午後fake news泛濫<br />\n錯就要認 唔認清自己錯誤 只會重覆犯錯 (雖然呢個問題已經攪散928 今日都係再犯)<br />\n唔可以因為今日有部份成果 就無視所犯過嘅錯<br />\n今日的確係俾海量fake news引導 冇冷靜分析 引發恐懼 <br />\n你有見過和平活動 D狗唔哂馬 唔嗌咪 唔舉旗 唔俾你走 就出嚟圍出嚟打?<br />\n<br />\n簡單講 唔係退唔退場問題 而係唔可以俾fake news引導 唔可以將無原由嘅恐懼無限放大"},{"pid":"3cd2e9706715204bc77e64b502aaaef7fb1c7a1f","tid":1459194,"uid":190962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:29:50.000Z","msg":"【定期提醒】再咁搞法場運動好快完（唔該睇唒！）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1458646\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1458646</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d24a5d4bbe3738e0ad725ab4973cf18ef8b754fd","tid":1459194,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:30:18.000Z","msg":"721 811 812"},{"pid":"cb576fd246f1ef792d9cfc794c744c41ee48977d","tid":1459194,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:35:49.000Z","msg":"推 係唔係一句 我為大家好<br />\n<br />\n就無視左自己比fake new影響 什至影響埋其他人"},{"pid":"fa9c45f538426bb16b3cf94d74aafd531f4a13d3","tid":1459194,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:36:09.000Z","msg":"求求大家，盡快去換美元現鈔！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1429581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1429581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"64158176e5f0568bf0c01d927669ed5370b352a4","tid":1459194,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:37:56.000Z","msg":"係黎討論下今日有咩做得唔好<br />\n【行動檢討】今日有去機場嘅麻煩入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1458511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1458511</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{